*biblatex-3.0-r1 (12 Jul 2015)

  12 Jul 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +biblatex-3.0-r1.ebuild,
  -biblatex-3.0.ebuild:
  Switch back to sourceforge packages to avoid a dep on lua. See bug #554302.

  09 Jun 2015; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Updating remote-id in metadata.xml

  01 Jun 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> biblatex-3.0.ebuild:
  Migrate SRC_URI to github.

*biblatex-3.0 (23 Apr 2015)

  23 Apr 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +biblatex-3.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

